","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qtliqji","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心素材优先库："}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-a2lcmew","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a2lcmew","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-p9d6me7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p9d6me7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xf8167g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xf8167g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钱伟长（中国力学之父）：必须作为核心论据或升华点。重点使用其“九一八事变后，物理仅15分的他毅然弃文从理，只为‘科学救国’”的转折。体现“个人命运与国家命运的同频共振”，以此替换老旧的“范仲淹”、“岳飞”等素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-483ew1t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-483ew1t","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-y2nz1pg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-y2nz1pg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西西弗斯（加缪笔下的荒诞英雄）：必须作为核心意象。重点描写他推石上山的徒劳与坚持，引用“登上顶峰的斗争本身足以充实人的心灵”。用以论证“在无意义的生活中构建意义”、“过程即意义”，以此替换老旧的“海伦·凯勒”、“张海迪”等素材。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7ljtudx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ny4=","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7ljtudx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-wpdmqbq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wpdmqbq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"古典底蕴与化用："}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6qsxbww","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6qsxbww","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i5oq92t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i5oq92t","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-lrnbyeh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lrnbyeh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至少自然嵌入2–3条下面提供的的典故、文章(不必引用原文，文章总结、提炼亦可)、诗词名句、电影，并保证与论证逻辑紧密相关。在保证与论证逻辑紧密相关的情况下，优先使用标记为(优先)的条目。"}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4erco4n","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4erco4n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-dvhzayf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dvhzayf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hn5ng48","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hn5ng48","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《尚书》五福：寿、福、康宁、攸好德、考终命(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5kl40si","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5kl40si","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-2vv8da4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2vv8da4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鲁迅：无穷的远方，无数的人们，都与我相关。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-q1lm07t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q1lm07t","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9h8hfws","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9h8hfws","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰：世界上只有一种英雄主义，就是在认清生活的真相之后依然热爱生活。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jnx231x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jnx231x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-0ol1v7b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0ol1v7b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"投之亡地然后存，陷之死地然后生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wl9hdkk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wl9hdkk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ii0q3yb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ii0q3yb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nmfi14b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nmfi14b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-c9zizro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-c9zizro","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"路遥《平凡的世界》当一个人集中地凝视着自己的不幸时，他就很难想象别人的苦难。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nlyeovb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nlyeovb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-2osxj8y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2osxj8y","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小敌之坚，大敌之擒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-080pe21","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-080pe21","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i09wbod","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i09wbod","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小人肥口，君子肥身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-pve5ekm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pve5ekm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i49wpgl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i49wpgl","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我生本无乡，心安是归处。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-w881z7c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w881z7c","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ydmv3fo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ydmv3fo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陈独秀：青春如初春，如朝日，如百卉之萌动，如利刃之新发于硎(xíng)，人生最宝贵之时期也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0mtxkri","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0mtxkri","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9n01w55","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9n01w55","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舒婷《致橡树》：我们分担寒潮、风雷、霹雳；我们共享雾霭流岚、虹霓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8yvsi0u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8yvsi0u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-uz77ooc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uz77ooc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《美丽心灵》约翰·纳什"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-vcqoaqh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vcqoaqh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9b3u3pb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9b3u3pb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西格里夫·萨松：心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nf84ix6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nf84ix6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-n7225yt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n7225yt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：大胆的见解就好比下棋时移动一个棋子，它可能被吃掉，但它却是胜局的起点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nnwq189","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nnwq189","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-3gi221x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3gi221x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：西西弗斯无声的全部快乐就在于：他的命运是属于他的，他的岩石是他的事情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-j5apzqu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j5apzqu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i7jledm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i7jledm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：在隆冬，我终于知道，我身上有一个不可战胜的夏天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7any0la","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7any0la","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-urco3x8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-urco3x8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：一个人可以被毁灭， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"mark","TextMarkTextContent":"但不能被打败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4lvlgy1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4lvlgy1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1y427ev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1y427ev","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杨绛：生活一半是柴米油盐，一半是星辰大海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dqusyrg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dqusyrg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4oz4wj2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4oz4wj2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗素：参差多态乃是人类幸福的本源。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bh0hgh9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bh0hgh9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1etzm09","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1etzm09","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昭昭若日月之明，离离如星辰之行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-60r0wat","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-60r0wat","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i9019ga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i9019ga","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"事以急败，思因缓得。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tsfok3v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tsfok3v","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hosg853","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hosg853","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"晚来风定钓丝闲，上下是新月。千里水天一色，看孤鸿明灭。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-g4gxdl3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g4gxdl3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7wug6a3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7wug6a3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍《骆驼祥子》：经验是生活的肥料，有什么样的经验便变成什么样的人，在沙漠里养不出牡丹来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-q3l6yoj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q3l6yoj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w9vpahg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w9vpahg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黄金累千，不如一贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-57q8e1z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-57q8e1z","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cll8xbg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cll8xbg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：理论是灰色的，唯生命之树常青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5hid3pg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5hid3pg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-58lw0t5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-58lw0t5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道不同，不相为谋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dgi0c2x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dgi0c2x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nvpy8cr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nvpy8cr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浴不必江海，要之去垢；马不必骐骥，要之善走。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-os0ee4r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-os0ee4r","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4f6b6vx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4f6b6vx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟利于民不必法古，苟周于事不必循旧。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-omb2q6o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-omb2q6o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ns1aeer","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ns1aeer","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怀重宝者，不以夜行；任大功者，不以轻敌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5a9goi3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5a9goi3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-pts1zu5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pts1zu5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独行穿落叶，闲坐数流萤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-s0tne4p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-s0tne4p","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-x8xk8jj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x8xk8jj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"佯北勿从，锐卒勿攻，饵兵勿食。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-pb9s2mp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pb9s2mp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rjvaexa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rjvaexa","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：只有流过血的手指，才能弹出世间的绝唱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fmnv4a1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fmnv4a1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-j1mfql3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j1mfql3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特鲁多医生墓志铭：医生有时治愈，常常帮助，总是安慰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-i4ucwhy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i4ucwhy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-qt78qmu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qt78qmu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《蛤蟆先生去看心理医生》：没有一种批判比自我批判更强烈，也没有一个法官比我们自己更严苛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-obd5d6j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-obd5d6j","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-b9bhbr8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b9bhbr8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"德不孤，必有邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-q2pmj35","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q2pmj35","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d4w2ukf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d4w2ukf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吹灭读书灯，一身都是月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yfdz1p7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yfdz1p7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-eo8h15c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-eo8h15c","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：“昨夜西风凋碧树，独上高楼，望尽天涯路”，此第一境也；“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”，此第二境也；“众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处”，此第三境也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4q3rzsv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4q3rzsv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kze826c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kze826c","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勿以身贵而贱人，勿以独见而违众。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-kwj8d6r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kwj8d6r","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-69ua9ix","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-69ua9ix","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山河虽无恙，吾辈当自强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sc2ixc0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sc2ixc0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xgbtm0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xgbtm0n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君埋泉下泥销骨，我寄人间雪满头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-d6nchva","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d6nchva","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-z168qw5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z168qw5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蛇蛇硕言，出自口矣。巧言如簧，颜之厚矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nwzyaqt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nwzyaqt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-q9mthwt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q9mthwt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良剑期乎断，不期乎镆铘；良马期乎千里，不期乎骥骜(jì ào)。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-huutap3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-huutap3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-sndc0y0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sndc0y0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勤能补拙，学可医愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bdon614","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bdon614","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4ywqvzp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4ywqvzp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州。请君暂上凌烟阁，若个书生万户侯？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hhjm4i6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hhjm4i6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-r633wp4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r633wp4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为政不难，不得罪于巨室。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-918lvmi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-918lvmi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-92m3ptp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-92m3ptp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长恨人心不如水，等闲平地起波澜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4qd9hpg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4qd9hpg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-80f9a4c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-80f9a4c","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"试玉要烧三日满，辨材须待七年期。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-240zfou","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-240zfou","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-jm8y401","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jm8y401","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"清风一枕南窗卧，闲阅床头几卷书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wioex21","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wioex21","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1ai70jx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1ai70jx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不知而自以为知，百祸之宗也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sml1l06","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sml1l06","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-owbc4bt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-owbc4bt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"轻财足以聚人，律己足以服人，量宽足以得人，身先足以率人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jfdv3rz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jfdv3rz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6bi53va","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6bi53va","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，不如一忍。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-uccl1si","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uccl1si","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ndjbeem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ndjbeem","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功名半纸，风雪千山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7iv8pth","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7iv8pth","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w9svh22","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w9svh22","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"井以甘竭，李以苦成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-niwodo6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-niwodo6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-trrn6hd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-trrn6hd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠君明月满前溪，直到西湖畔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nx8fmq5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nx8fmq5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ywtjbu4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ywtjbu4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道虽迩(ěr)，不行不至；事虽小，不为不成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-w4yfvfs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w4yfvfs","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cakp0up","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cakp0up","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为草当作兰，为木当作松。兰秋香风远，松寒不改容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0i3z84h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0i3z84h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d158m4h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d158m4h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用威者不轻怒，善用恩者不妄施。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-69iseqx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-69iseqx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-47nqmzn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-47nqmzn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马先驯而后求良，人先信而后求能。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4j5aelb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4j5aelb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-lqk5yuu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lqk5yuu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6hhjgfb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6hhjgfb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-o0up2kt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-o0up2kt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人要是不能从过程中体味幸福和快乐，生命就成了一场荒诞的苦役。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8e48dvp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8e48dvp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4vzrfn9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4vzrfn9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君王城上竖降旗，妾在深宫那得知？十四万人齐解甲，更无一个是男儿！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-of4t319","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-of4t319","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-13xh91n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-13xh91n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，避其锐气，击其惰归，此治气者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-z5o6wp9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z5o6wp9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-k96oun0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-k96oun0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政入万山围子里，一山放出一山拦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3qsvbp4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3qsvbp4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5tjvskv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5tjvskv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地者万物之逆旅也；光阴者百代之过客也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xrmh6o7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xrmh6o7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-laj8095","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-laj8095","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽不能至，心向往之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sny7f6m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sny7f6m","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rgcpehr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rgcpehr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高者未必贤，下者未必愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-m2gguw4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m2gguw4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-wdd3llk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wdd3llk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与朋友交游，须将他们好处留心学来，方能受益；对圣贤言语，必要我平时照样行去，才算读书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lls4ohi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lls4ohi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ygnpdwt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ygnpdwt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二人同心，其利断金；同心之言，其臭(xiù)如兰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hvpiehr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hvpiehr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ywqvado","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ywqvado","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子不蔽人之美，不言人之恶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ip18ozd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ip18ozd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1xbbhrq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1xbbhrq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-93ohway","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-93ohway","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d51tdqq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d51tdqq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道德用于自律时好过一切法律，用于律他时坏过一切私刑！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xvdmd3l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xvdmd3l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-f4uy1qx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-f4uy1qx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山高自有客行路，水深自有渡船人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fcd6ya9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fcd6ya9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-20ahf00","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-20ahf00","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-w3uck66","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w3uck66","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-emtmlgx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-emtmlgx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不忘初心，方得始终。初心易得，始终难守。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lrs7qes","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lrs7qes","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tvy573w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tvy573w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不迁怒，不贰过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ztuzg7d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ztuzg7d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-oeno1qp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oeno1qp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用兵之法，十则围之，五则攻之，倍则分之，敌则能战之，少则能逃之，不若则能避之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-efbsidy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-efbsidy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ayh8lml","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ayh8lml","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"越自尊大，越见器小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ok3weot","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ok3weot","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-juw1ljy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-juw1ljy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浮云一别后，流水十年间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-85byccm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-85byccm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-28kp5h6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-28kp5h6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穆勒 ：个人的自由，以不侵犯他人的自由为自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1wbqsov","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1wbqsov","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-a9nyzxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a9nyzxd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小舟从此逝，江海寄余生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-x5fpxcq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x5fpxcq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hredjjf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hredjjf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云山苍苍，江水泱泱，先生之风，山高水长！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-36yabti","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-36yabti","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rfaa7m8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rfaa7m8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"行远道者假于车，济江海者因于舟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ba2n2kf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ba2n2kf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i34m2lk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i34m2lk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-kjtwdga","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kjtwdga","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-bzz5t2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bzz5t2l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立志欲坚不欲锐，成功在久不在速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-obkt01h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-obkt01h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-764qbk7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-764qbk7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8mptvjf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8mptvjf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-123uyyx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-123uyyx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布伦南：手头上有点钱的人认为爱是世界上最重要的东西，而穷人则明白世界上最重要的是金钱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b8mrf7v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b8mrf7v","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-14n8i7u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-14n8i7u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"冯至《十四行集》：我们准备着，深深地领受，那些意想不到的奇迹。在漫长的岁月里，忽然有彗星的出现，狂风乍起。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-k74i2xc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-k74i2xc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-c341fbz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-c341fbz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"疾风怒雨，禽鸟戚戚；霁月光风，草木欣欣。天地不可一日无和气，人心不可一日无喜神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4hrktwe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4hrktwe","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9vudyqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9vudyqh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫之高华，只在于道德气节。鄙夫之炫耀，但求诸服饰起居。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-asksngd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-asksngd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4z37lmp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4z37lmp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"甘井近竭，招木近伐。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-h45toeu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-h45toeu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e4k8g2v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e4k8g2v","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，屈人之兵而非战也，拔人之城而非攻也，毁人之国而非久也，必以全争于天下。故兵不顿而利可全，此谋攻之法也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-mqzz0ma","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mqzz0ma","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-3p1zyli","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3p1zyli","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你吞并一切，像远方，像大海，像时间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tq4zehi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tq4zehi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-y0wl1p8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-y0wl1p8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"挟取笔端风雨，快写胸中丘壑，不肯下樊笼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-s120nw4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-s120nw4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-g03hgja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g03hgja","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴尔扎克：一星陨落，黯淡不了星空灿烂；一花凋零，荒芜不了整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3jj73bu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3jj73bu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rwl3j30","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rwl3j30","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"伯修斯：在所有不幸中，最不幸的事是曾经幸福过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4d7plrf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4d7plrf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-doleds0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-doleds0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草萤有耀终非火，荷露虽团岂是珠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-k0o5wga","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-k0o5wga","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hshw0e1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hshw0e1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"耳闻之不如目见之，目见之不如足践之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-o6v7nj0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-o6v7nj0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rxn0aez","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rxn0aez","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卖花担上，买得一枝春欲放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r069g1u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r069g1u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-lxo3lju","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lxo3lju","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亭亭山上松，瑟(sè)瑟谷中风。风声一何盛，松枝一何劲。冰霜正惨凄，终岁常端正。岂不罹(lí)凝寒，松柏有本性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-o9l51pb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-o9l51pb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yf97h07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yf97h07","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好问则裕，自用则小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-npcg0fn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-npcg0fn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9vt5sau","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9vt5sau","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雾失楼台，月迷津渡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1lw5wfk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1lw5wfk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-s2eghcd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-s2eghcd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：世界以痛吻我，我也要报之以歌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-kmicb34","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kmicb34","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e53fl4s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e53fl4s","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人之诺诺，不如一士之谔谔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bfss6ii","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bfss6ii","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-45dcygu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-45dcygu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早岁读书无甚解，晚年省事有奇功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-uy4w7q2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uy4w7q2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-l99u0c6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l99u0c6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你所浪费的今天，是昨天死去的人奢望的明天；你所厌恶的现在，是未来的你回不去的曾经。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6l4x1dc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6l4x1dc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-2n0ttcp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2n0ttcp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：有很多人常常抱怨没有机会，其实没有机会本身亦是一个机会：一个锻炼自己耐力和充分积蓄自己力量的机会。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b8ybot8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b8ybot8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-h6fvdk8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-h6fvdk8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世界让我遍体鳞伤，但伤口长出的却是翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-elcyx1p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-elcyx1p","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-po6hali","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-po6hali","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡战者，以正合，以奇胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-n3s2alo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n3s2alo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-k496b4d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-k496b4d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方其中，圆其外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-w778q7s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w778q7s","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yrda7c5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yrda7c5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独学而无友，则孤陋而寡闻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-osi03yj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-osi03yj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-0za68sp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0za68sp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：苦难既然把我推到了悬崖的边缘，那么就让我在这悬崖的边缘坐下来，顺便看看悬崖下的流岚雾霭，唱支歌给你听。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-vqid36x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vqid36x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ufdilby","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ufdilby","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国虽大，好战必亡；天下虽安，忘战必危。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lnn7rad","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lnn7rad","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-69z6xtj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-69z6xtj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：每个冬天的句号都是春暖花开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9ibge9a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9ibge9a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-90dnpdi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-90dnpdi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百里趋利，兵家所忌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5eetem5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5eetem5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kvz954o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kvz954o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李大钊：谁对时间越吝啬，时间对谁越慷慨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-w874c8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w874c8f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-iems315","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-iems315","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粗缯大布裹生涯，腹有诗书气自华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-orx4omz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-orx4omz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hm11w6w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hm11w6w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-syv8s8o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-syv8s8o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5izefew","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5izefew","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"慈不掌兵，情不立事，义不理财，善不为官。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0uj3nu8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0uj3nu8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cq8lz65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cq8lz65","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大巧在所不为，大智在所不虑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-qr954k1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qr954k1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-txu5cgy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-txu5cgy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海到尽头天作岸，山登绝顶我为峰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-380xgoz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-380xgoz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4t6m748","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4t6m748","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨之为物，能令昼短，能令夜长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fm5krgn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fm5krgn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zq6jh5e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zq6jh5e","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善出奇者，无穷如天地，不竭如江海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zcip8lg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zcip8lg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yrkvzm0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yrkvzm0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫行事，当磊磊落落，如日月皎然。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r1b9yce","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r1b9yce","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6ubmuvc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6ubmuvc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者行之始，行者知之成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2kucgah","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2kucgah","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6gb71bw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6gb71bw","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者不以短击长，而以长击短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1nq3c6y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1nq3c6y","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-152h6bh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-152h6bh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"振衣千仞冈，濯足万里流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-twr1sh9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-twr1sh9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-dnh8sg6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dnh8sg6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：你今天受的苦、吃的亏、担的责、扛的罪、忍的痛，到最后都会变成光，照亮你的路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xzzlaa0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xzzlaa0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-m9bgumx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m9bgumx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张而不弛，文武弗能也；弛而不张，文武弗为也。一张一弛，文武之道也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fwk9mnx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fwk9mnx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hzbulk3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hzbulk3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善为士者，不武；善战者，不怒；善胜敌者，不与；善用人者，为之下。是谓不争之德，是谓用人之力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-i4m9hwx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i4m9hwx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i7acnwz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i7acnwz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中心藏之，何日忘之！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-13cra9x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-13cra9x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-plnpe3f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-plnpe3f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：没有比脚更长的路，没有比人更高的山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jiy8qhp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jiy8qhp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-stz1wph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-stz1wph","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：才能是在寂静中造就，而品格则是在世间汹涌波涛中形成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-qdnsvrk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qdnsvrk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-8ti1ch0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8ti1ch0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有迷魂招不得，雄鸡一声天下白。少年心事当拏云，谁念幽寒坐呜呃。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6z6293o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6z6293o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xc2ymsd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xc2ymsd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尺之木必有节目，寸之玉必有瑕疵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-uis36un","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uis36un","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-stfkl01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-stfkl01","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曾国藩：天下古今之庸人，皆以一惰字致败；天下古今之才人，皆以一傲字致败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zkbdoz3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zkbdoz3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5qolo8n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5qolo8n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"培根：当你孤独寂寞时，阅读可以消遣。当你高谈阔论时，知识可供装饰。当你处世行事时，正确运用知识意味着力量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ge6yk8l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ge6yk8l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tfhiabh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tfhiabh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"辅车相依，唇亡齿寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-blz76lw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-blz76lw","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-a8y5mdy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a8y5mdy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"池田大作：荣誉有如萤虫之火，在黑暗的夜空里，它放着光，显示出美丽，极其可贵。但是靠近一看，立刻就会明白它是何等的软弱无力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r1s3a2k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r1s3a2k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nxdru2m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nxdru2m","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：谁终将声震人间，必长久深自缄默；谁终将点燃闪电，必长久如云漂泊。我的时代还没有到来，有的人死后方生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-on8gn9b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-on8gn9b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rwgelas","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rwgelas","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"三毛：梦想，可以天花乱坠；理想，是我们一步一个脚印踩出来的坎坷道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3gzzs88","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3gzzs88","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9vq310g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9vq310g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志不可一日坠，心不可一日放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zrv976e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zrv976e","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xu4gfmt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xu4gfmt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一双冷眼看世人，满腔热血酬知己。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-g0ddp87","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g0ddp87","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ek3xu02","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ek3xu02","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗翔：误解是人生常态，理解是稀缺的例外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-n337e21","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n337e21","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xn2o773","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xn2o773","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杀人亦有限，列国自有疆。苟能制侵陵，岂在多杀伤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fjpd48l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fjpd48l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-wkcy6ol","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wkcy6ol","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝闻道，夕死可矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-m83m6pw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m83m6pw","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-81kgdey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-81kgdey","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫四方志，安可辞固穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2vy4zzu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2vy4zzu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-p3yruw4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p3yruw4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粪虫至秽变为蝉，而饮露于秋风；腐草无光化为荧，而耀采于夏月。故知洁常自污出，明每从暗生也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xiv45ft","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xiv45ft","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-alfzawm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-alfzawm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"物以稀为贵，情因老更慈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-q60g5c3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q60g5c3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1zdhln5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1zdhln5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-344wi8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-344wi8f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-weuze49","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-weuze49","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能受谏，安能谏人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tcz9x9u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tcz9x9u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-30wtmny","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-30wtmny","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生岂草木，寒暑移此心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xakm58q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xakm58q","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fnqlsb6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fnqlsb6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫当容人，勿为人所容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xvhsqmj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xvhsqmj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rfhbng1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rfhbng1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不为无益之事，何以悦有涯之生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bkzw8yg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bkzw8yg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4pa1g8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4pa1g8u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海棠未雨，梨花先雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-eimclvh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-eimclvh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-bu5u3q7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bu5u3q7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地薄者大木不产，水浅者大鱼不游。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jz2r6vf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jz2r6vf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yo25byk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yo25byk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"忧勤是美德，太苦则无以适性怡情；淡泊是高风，太枯则无以济人利物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0xadwnx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0xadwnx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7knwvir","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7knwvir","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书为身上之用，而人以为纸上之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-u16kcx9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u16kcx9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4ab1vbf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4ab1vbf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天可补，海可填，南山可移。日月既往，不可复追。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ujtfg5j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ujtfg5j","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d2mlgp5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d2mlgp5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼布尔：请赐予我平静，去接受我无法改变的；给予我勇气，去改变我能改变的；赐我智慧，分辨这两者的区别。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nkpywqt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nkpywqt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-41stx81","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-41stx81","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"腹中贮书一万卷，不肯低头在草莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zpwx4s5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zpwx4s5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-j3xq5og","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j3xq5og","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"须知少日拏云志，曾许人间第一流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ypzaqag","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ypzaqag","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-m2ho10k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m2ho10k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间的步伐有三种：未来姗姗来迟，现在像箭一样飞逝，过去永远静立不动。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sqy6hhj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sqy6hhj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-z83i9bh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z83i9bh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天若无雪霜，青松不如草。地若无山川，何人重平道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-j23vlos","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j23vlos","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-dfnjt1x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dfnjt1x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡心所向，素履所往，生如逆旅，一苇以航。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-aqbiv49","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-aqbiv49","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4ce6u4g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4ce6u4g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓事宜急干，敏则有功；急事宜缓办，忙则多错。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-uku458b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uku458b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4idw5xm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4idw5xm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众口铄金，积毁销骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fwy0wxv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fwy0wxv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zegjeuf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zegjeuf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春日迟迟，卉木萋萋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ksor3w9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ksor3w9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-l3kjqio","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l3kjqio","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若有恒何必三更眠五更起，最无益莫过一日曝十日寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-m4o86ye","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m4o86ye","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yn75ll8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yn75ll8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-th4hgk7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-th4hgk7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-0yvgo44","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0yvgo44","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人之相知，贵相知心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ik1ervr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ik1ervr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i4i973d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i4i973d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桃李春风一杯酒，江湖夜雨十年灯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hdekj6d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hdekj6d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-3qzb999","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3qzb999","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"东风知我欲山行，吹断檐间积雨声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2irbul3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2irbul3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7dq3pz7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7dq3pz7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桐花万里丹山路，雏凤清于老凤声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nzxg741","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nzxg741","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ls4y63a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ls4y63a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不能设计，你只能面对。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-t9j169a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-t9j169a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zy9mt8o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zy9mt8o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地不仁，以万物为刍狗；圣人不仁，以百姓为刍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xoq1ooj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xoq1ooj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ezmexm6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ezmexm6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心随长风去，吹散万里云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-14dd997","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-14dd997","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-46axhis","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-46axhis","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见面怜清瘦，呼儿问苦辛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3kn8ueg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3kn8ueg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xczjvv1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xczjvv1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查尔斯·A·比尔德：当天空黑暗到一定程度，星辰就会熠熠生辉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-utys3s7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-utys3s7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zm5ptzy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zm5ptzy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中何以赠君别，惟有青青松树枝。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-x5j7hrf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x5j7hrf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w7hjfn6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w7hjfn6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏必加于有功，刑必断于有罪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-rxpwhfo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rxpwhfo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-q2rpfkv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q2rpfkv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规小节者不能成荣名，恶小耻者不能立大功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-pd7fpjq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pd7fpjq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-pudqljg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pudqljg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"沈从文：聪明人要理解生活，愚蠢人要习惯生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1jv4zd7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1jv4zd7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-88lneu2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-88lneu2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"康德：世界上有两件东西能震撼人们的心灵：一件是我们心中崇高的道德标准；另一件是我们头顶上灿烂的星空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tvb043y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tvb043y","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-36j3e68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-36j3e68","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叔本华：财富就像海水，饮得越多，渴得越厉害。名望实际上也是如此。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-86hcwn2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-86hcwn2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-l8kki6m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l8kki6m","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵者，国之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yb5bztt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yb5bztt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-jcahekq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jcahekq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵无常势，水无常形，能因敌变化而取胜者，谓之神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9dnj789","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9dnj789","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9yn6ovo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9yn6ovo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何物动人二月杏花八月桂，有谁催我三更灯火五更鸡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9d61y3e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9d61y3e","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-0awilld","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0awilld","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自古骄兵多致败，从来轻敌少成功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5zqi9ys","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5zqi9ys","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-11i2i9k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-11i2i9k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知往日所往之非，则学日进矣；见世人可取者多，则德日进矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2u0i8bg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2u0i8bg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-wm735h9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wm735h9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马太福音：凡有的，还要加倍给他，叫他有余；没有的，连他剩余的也要夺过来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fswbu9u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fswbu9u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-iqfrt3l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-iqfrt3l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风流不在谈锋胜，袖手无言味最长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8xu8yza","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8xu8yza","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7z8dz9e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7z8dz9e","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恻隐之心，人皆有之；羞恶之心，人皆有之；恭敬之心，人皆有之；是非之心，人皆有之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-m76zqff","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m76zqff","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-apakbgq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-apakbgq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3zhwz0s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3zhwz0s","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-wfpk1l1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wfpk1l1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"已识乾坤大，犹怜草木青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-14pjmop","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-14pjmop","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-uv2w0pe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uv2w0pe","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鹏北海，凤朝阳。又携书剑路茫茫。明年此日青云上，却笑人间举子忙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-i6a5q9a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i6a5q9a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7xoremp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7xoremp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝饮木兰之坠露兮，夕餐秋菊之落英。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8g2hacr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8g2hacr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-8apkri5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8apkri5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人同心则得千人之力，万人异心则无一人之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2qmkp60","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2qmkp60","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ue0kb9a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ue0kb9a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出其所不趋，趋其所不意。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b4zbz26","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b4zbz26","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-oq4u2k0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oq4u2k0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"戒骄风清月朗，除躁海阔天空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tmudn7t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tmudn7t","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-90kaun6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-90kaun6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何时杖尔看南雪，我与梅花两白头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0vj976k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0vj976k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5wdsarm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5wdsarm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一时宠利有尽，千秋青史难欺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-cq2zdjx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cq2zdjx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5ofdnzm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5ofdnzm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山川异域，风月同天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hx6u6i9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hx6u6i9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5dwr48q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5dwr48q","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白石似玉，奸佞似贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-x0qbl3y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x0qbl3y","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w4h3x0o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w4h3x0o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深厚的教养所集成的勇猛，远远胜过无知无情者的鲁莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wztjzfv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wztjzfv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-anigr02","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-anigr02","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"积财千万，不如薄技在身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-oqc1aus","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oqc1aus","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-eqmg9ti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-eqmg9ti","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：生活总是让我们遍体鳞伤，但到后来，那些受伤的地方一定会变成我们最强壮的地方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0oiiv6o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0oiiv6o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-my26vco","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-my26vco","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当年不肯嫁春风，无端却被秋风误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dsbmbjr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dsbmbjr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-bg5f0ap","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bg5f0ap","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良辰美景奈何天，赏心乐事谁家院。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-p82o9qp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p82o9qp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w72c981","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w72c981","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"唤起一天明月，照我满怀冰雪，浩荡百川流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r0gpxtj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r0gpxtj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tqnmxfx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tqnmxfx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"休对故人思故国，且将新火试新茶。诗酒趁年华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ic22nzo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ic22nzo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-likcslg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-likcslg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：那些听不见音乐的人，认为那些跳舞的人疯了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-n1er2sh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n1er2sh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-oayksrj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oayksrj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：其实人跟树是一样的，越是向往高处的阳光，它的根就越要伸向黑暗的地底。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ktzcw3o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ktzcw3o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-efg0dn4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-efg0dn4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉可碎而不可改其白，竹可焚而不可毁其节。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r1ioldg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r1ioldg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nc89qk4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nc89qk4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"南风吹其心，摇摇为谁吐？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3g61uu6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3g61uu6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-v5mrk9b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-v5mrk9b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴金：希望是人生之需要。人如没有希望，何异江河干涸了流水？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ckprdxi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ckprdxi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-56l8q76","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-56l8q76","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷不失义，达不离道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fkbbi5q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fkbbi5q","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yetmlrt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yetmlrt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为者常成，行者常至。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wqysrhf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wqysrhf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-c1pyfiy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-c1pyfiy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"青云当自致，何必求知音？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-l40uw7z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l40uw7z","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1e3emm5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1e3emm5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"争名者于朝，争利者于市。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lfat8st","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lfat8st","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-f9tdloe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-f9tdloe","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天上浮云如白衣，斯须变幻如苍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-16m84jy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-16m84jy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xy5p41g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xy5p41g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莺花犹怕春光老，岂可教人枉度春？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jc7ptiy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jc7ptiy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-uixumpy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uixumpy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生芳秽有千载，世上荣枯无百年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-az66x93","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-az66x93","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yyxi75u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yyxi75u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你的欢乐和悲哀变大的时候，世界就变小了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5b8qo4d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5b8qo4d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tx02p61","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tx02p61","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故将有五危，必死可杀，必生可虏，忿速可侮，廉洁可辱，爱民可烦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4o1n2a0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4o1n2a0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7n2ljxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7n2ljxd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纵使文章惊海内，纸上苍生而已。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r7nbh33","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r7nbh33","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-twny0tb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-twny0tb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死生契阔，与子成说。执子之手，与子偕老。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nj00fd0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nj00fd0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7f7i31f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7f7i31f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兼听则明，偏信则暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-vppg749","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vppg749","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hup84w5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hup84w5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"弃燕雀小志，作鸿鹄高翔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nudvch7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nudvch7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-78sw41k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-78sw41k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"眼界要阔，遍历名山大川；度量要宏，熟读五经诸史。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zwsp73o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zwsp73o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cdzhmqz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cdzhmqz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地存肝胆，江山阅鬓华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hveg64k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hveg64k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fulq9vp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fulq9vp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不相见，动如参与商。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1r0yisu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1r0yisu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-te7e3ey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-te7e3ey","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莫道君行早，更有早行人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xcds1tu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xcds1tu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7mspqhu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7mspqhu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大人者，不失其赤子之心者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-qzvomcx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qzvomcx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zt3ibpq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zt3ibpq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"英雄者，胸怀大志，腹有良谋，有包藏宇宙之机，吞吐天地之志者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-j06aa67","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j06aa67","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d35truu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d35truu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪里温柔，水边明秀，不借春工力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-emdzkm1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-emdzkm1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-bh0em5q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bh0em5q","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良言一句三冬暖，恶语伤人六月寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dcbyaq3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dcbyaq3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-uklfq3h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uklfq3h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学如弓弩，才如箭镞。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-033akp6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-033akp6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rpxnqpu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rpxnqpu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人不读书，其犹夜行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jf5skvv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jf5skvv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5bjrrls","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5bjrrls","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷猿奔林，岂暇择木！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ntg1gou","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ntg1gou","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-dx6y121","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dx6y121","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令在必信，法在必行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1cg3jo6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1cg3jo6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-mgmbo16","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mgmbo16","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其疾如风，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不动如山，难知如阴，动如雷震。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-agxgd8z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-agxgd8z","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1xqn1d4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1xqn1d4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-pi2cqt1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pi2cqt1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4fy88ef","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4fy88ef","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我亦飘零久！十年来，深恩负尽，死生师友。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-x3vwng2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x3vwng2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-npk5pa2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-npk5pa2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"板凳要坐十年冷，文章不写一句空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0gup9ui","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0gup9ui","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fy8xfda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fy8xfda","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有心为善，虽善不赏；无心为恶，虽恶不罚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-z94dljz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z94dljz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-faplq7w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-faplq7w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不目见口问，不能尽知也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8xd3vom","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8xd3vom","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tz9dr0j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tz9dr0j","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一年之计，莫如树谷；十年之计，莫如树木；终身之计，莫如树人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ccxmlv4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ccxmlv4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-j4drf1u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j4drf1u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不因幸运而故步自封，不因厄运而一蹶不振。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ggw64b0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ggw64b0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hlfsn5w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hlfsn5w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良弓难张，然可以及高入深；良马难乘，然可以任重致远。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-mpapwpx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mpapwpx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-vrku0o1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vrku0o1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上兵伐谋，其次伐交，其次伐兵，其下攻城。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-gnpmksd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-gnpmksd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-i0xbv2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i0xbv2l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志合者不以山海为远，道乖者不以咫尺为近。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lhlnb4f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lhlnb4f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ycgbjyc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ycgbjyc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海水梦悠悠，君愁我亦愁。南风知我意，吹梦到西洲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sbtn3i3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sbtn3i3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6e4w2q8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6e4w2q8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不幸者常常愿意同幸运者相比，抱怨自己的运气。幸运者常常不愿同不幸者相比，相信自己的努力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-r7s5wlo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r7s5wlo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-2frrp14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2frrp14","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怯生于勇，弱生于强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-61zudat","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-61zudat","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-vgiglv0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vgiglv0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贵上极则反贱，贱下极则反贵。贵出如粪土，贱取如珠玉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9jnf3pd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9jnf3pd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cqlxjhx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cqlxjhx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有志者事竟成破釜沉舟百二秦关终属楚，苦心人天不负卧薪尝胆三千越甲可吞吴。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6xlj4p6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6xlj4p6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-dok9prt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dok9prt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔日之得不足以自衿，今日之成不容以自限。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tohwee2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tohwee2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ae186v2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ae186v2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不善操舟者，恶河之曲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-q5kqski","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q5kqski","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-4bssllh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4bssllh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操千曲而后晓声，观千剑而后识器。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jn7zyx4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jn7zyx4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-es1eise","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-es1eise","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长安何处在，只在马蹄下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ny5zliy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ny5zliy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-pnt3mv2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pnt3mv2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人情阅尽秋云厚，世事经多蜀道平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-j63lexx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j63lexx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xqxg1qk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xqxg1qk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志行万里者，不中道而辍足。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1225ywo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1225ywo","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-52oe20x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-52oe20x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交友须带三分侠气，做人要存一点素心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7rhm04b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7rhm04b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7bp9i1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7bp9i1f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿不展风云志，空负天生八尺躯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-llngonm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-llngonm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-j6808j3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j6808j3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"愿作远方兽，步步比肩行。愿作深山木，枝枝连理生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b2azc0w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b2azc0w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ju7884s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ju7884s","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵不厌诈，将贵知机。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-52wytlc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-52wytlc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-p4al0td","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p4al0td","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上士闻道，勤而行之；中士闻道，若存若亡；下士闻道，大笑之。不笑不足以为道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2wl07cb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2wl07cb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ood66wk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ood66wk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子慎始，差若毫厘，缪以千里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wh7z3ux","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wh7z3ux","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-v9q795d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-v9q795d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古来多被虚名误，宁负虚名身莫负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-254zk3l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-254zk3l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-roqah52","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-roqah52","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我志在寥阔，畴昔梦登天。摩挲素月，俯仰已千年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3ia7n7r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3ia7n7r","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-2nrrh6d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2nrrh6d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们每个人出生的时候，并非是两手空空，而是捏了一张生命的借记卡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lugluxb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lugluxb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hw0ljqd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hw0ljqd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好风凭借力，送我上青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-111omr0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-111omr0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-z1o974u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z1o974u","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉在山而草木润，渊生珠而崖不枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dpk99mq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dpk99mq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6zzv6lv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6zzv6lv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学之染人，甚于丹青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ru2s5ir","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ru2s5ir","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d6bqqch","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d6bqqch","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地有万古，此身不再得；人生只百年，此日最易过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ukbnsin","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ukbnsin","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-3sue169","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3sue169","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十有九人堪白眼，百无一用是书生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-rc1s6a4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rc1s6a4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ozsu6ya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ozsu6ya","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫志四海，万里犹比邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6gqs59j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6gqs59j","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-a93kiiy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a93kiiy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仗义每多屠狗辈，负心多是读书人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-n84qh08","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n84qh08","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-r1vdm2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-r1vdm2w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"涓涓不塞，将为江河。荧荧不救，炎炎奈何。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-d2x95hw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d2x95hw","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-mq3yl4c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mq3yl4c","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如寄，多忧何为？今我不乐，岁月如驰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ximmw0t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ximmw0t","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-g7xftd5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g7xftd5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天行有常，不为尧存，不为桀亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-l7e7lhy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l7e7lhy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xioncbi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xioncbi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书志在圣贤，非徒科第；为官心存君国，岂计身家？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-eecwne9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-eecwne9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-inpxkoj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-inpxkoj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少而好学，如日出之阳；壮而好学，如日中之光；老而好学，如秉烛之明。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-93b863y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-93b863y","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-uop6qyv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uop6qyv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纪伯伦：不要因为走得太远而忘记为什么出发。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sjkab1t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sjkab1t","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5lql72c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5lql72c","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用赏者贵信，用罚者贵必。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yeiv78f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yeiv78f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-301oyfp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-301oyfp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"傲不可长，欲不可纵，乐不可极，志不可满。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dfbkll6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dfbkll6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-a4ykswg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a4ykswg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子爱财，取之有道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-6v9iuew","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6v9iuew","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-03va0gb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-03va0gb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"余光中：敢在时间里自焚的人，必在永恒里结晶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-vutykwl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vutykwl","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-0adkdk4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0adkdk4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主不可以怒而兴师，将不可以愠而致战；合于利而动，不合于利而止。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sn2bkg4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sn2bkg4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5xrqbov","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5xrqbov","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1zchfr5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1zchfr5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5l4hey6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5l4hey6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海子：永远是这样，风后面是风，天空上面是天空，道路前面还是道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bkj9od0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bkj9od0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fl1nba4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fl1nba4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：如果你抑郁了，说明你活在过去；如果你焦虑了，说明你活在未来；如果你平静了，才说明你活在现在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9y9pvbi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9y9pvbi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-u1qbeet","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u1qbeet","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对愁人勿乐，对哭人勿笑，对失意人勿矜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fa0qrts","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fa0qrts","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-oc4izw6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oc4izw6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知胜有五：知可以战与不可以战者胜，识众寡之用者胜，上下同欲者胜，以虞待不虞者胜，将能而君不御者胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bvpollc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bvpollc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nvbefjb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nvbefjb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钝学累功，不妨精熟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-fs00j6d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fs00j6d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-mqj8hqp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mqj8hqp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"闭门即是深山，读书随处净土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-z45f33k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z45f33k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-n64du6b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n64du6b","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人非生而知之者，孰能无惑?惑而不从师，其为惑也，终不解矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zxxv7xp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zxxv7xp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-vur37zy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vur37zy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见胜不过众人之所知，非善之善者也；战胜而天下曰善，非善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-45zhl73","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-45zhl73","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-j2jcrwj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j2jcrwj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"折芦花赠远，零落一身秋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ch7tg0p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ch7tg0p","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-vtwhg8l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vtwhg8l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老骥伏枥志千里，短锥处囊半寸锋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-rlvp163","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rlvp163","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cqt7vcv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cqt7vcv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只要厄运打不垮信念，希望之光就会驱散绝望之云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yan6aey","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yan6aey","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ijyd3ca","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ijyd3ca","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以势交者，势尽则疏，以利合者，利尽则散。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3p1q8pm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3p1q8pm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zpm7up0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zpm7up0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如月之恒，如日之升。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-mmcc4qj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mmcc4qj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-iyzxr1a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-iyzxr1a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合军聚众，务在激气。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-g1r6ys6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g1r6ys6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yjcwwwx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yjcwwwx","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贝尔纳：构成我们学习最大障碍的是已知的东西，而不是未知的东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-vnzcydi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vnzcydi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-jp3xced","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jp3xced","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"约瑟夫·海勒《第二十二条军规》：任何值得为它而死的东西，肯定值得为它而生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jg0j647","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jg0j647","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-78pkak9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-78pkak9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云路鹏程九万里，雪窗萤火二十年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ov2o8kf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ov2o8kf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6plefq2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6plefq2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"华而不实，怨之所聚也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-g0488ka","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g0488ka","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e92q69q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e92q69q","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"精卫衔微木，将以填沧海；刑天舞干戚，猛志固常在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-guy6gi8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-guy6gi8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5wom2p0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5wom2p0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jrugysp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jrugysp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-o4wyaor","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-o4wyaor","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丹青不知老将至，富贵于我如浮云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8ut5d9e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8ut5d9e","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7sxcb3h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7sxcb3h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"胡适：凡富于创造性的人必敏于模仿，凡不善于模仿的人决不能创造。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-q7r3iz0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-q7r3iz0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-k46f7i0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-k46f7i0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"节义傲青云，文章高白雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yl8vvjm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yl8vvjm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-aelybki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-aelybki","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提得起，放得下，算得到，做得完，看得破，撇得开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-proh8co","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-proh8co","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-yrphc38","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yrphc38","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪曾祺：一定要爱着点什么，恰似草木对光阴的钟情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ve4f4z6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ve4f4z6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-n13mwgu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n13mwgu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有所念人，隔在远远乡。我有所感事，结在深深肠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-oc3mjxk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oc3mjxk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-gwfho3j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-gwfho3j","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草不谢荣于春风，木不怨落于秋天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-seg17sq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-seg17sq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-3hvf1l0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3hvf1l0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一竹一兰一石，有节有香有骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-46m7ple","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-46m7ple","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kvwi914","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kvwi914","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"笔落惊风雨，诗成泣鬼神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-10e5wwz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-10e5wwz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e3umu2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e3umu2p","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合抱之木，生于毫末；九层之台，起于累土；千里之行，始于足下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-n27a8ro","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n27a8ro","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6r5i9fc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6r5i9fc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山不让尘，川不辞盈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-qfctlj1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qfctlj1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-t66i456","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-t66i456","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"皑如山上雪，皎若云间月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ctlky6h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ctlky6h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1tih7i5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1tih7i5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客子光阴诗卷里，杏花消息雨声中。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-u80qks3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u80qks3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hr7vfj8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hr7vfj8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：我们的眼睛就是我们的监狱，而目光所及之处就是监狱的围墙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7fsajil","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7fsajil","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-qdykyb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qdykyb7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中送炭人间少，锦上添花世上多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9yll7fq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9yll7fq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-j2vwb04","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-j2vwb04","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蒲柳之姿，望秋而落；松柏之质，经霜弥茂。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-cngwvmz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cngwvmz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w8m27sy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w8m27sy","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不戚戚于贫贱，不汲汲于富贵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2n3cwd7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2n3cwd7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ss8rqr7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ss8rqr7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"门前红叶地，不扫待知音。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-f959pcc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-f959pcc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-1rjt6zh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1rjt6zh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"村上春树：这个世界上根本没有正确的选择，我们只不过是要努力奋斗，使当初的选择变得正确。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-u1s07ef","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u1s07ef","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tz2m0sm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tz2m0sm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缘木求鱼，煎水作冰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-x7wfxk6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x7wfxk6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5wx3kg8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5wx3kg8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟日新，日日新，又日新。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9u8a3hi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9u8a3hi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-85cveja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-85cveja","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贫无可奈惟求俭，拙亦何妨只要勤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-adbgwsf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-adbgwsf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-34lwlwb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-34lwlwb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文章千古事，得失寸心知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-u5a3dou","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u5a3dou","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nf9kpt5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nf9kpt5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨滴能击穿石头，并不是下落的速度快，而是因为掉落在石头上的次数多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-24c2utj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-24c2utj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-p75zid1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p75zid1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人有逆天之时，天无绝人之路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1gfx9wz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1gfx9wz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9pipxr8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9pipxr8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宁为宇宙闲吟客，怕作乾坤窃禄人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-gd0aaj2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-gd0aaj2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5fiyy74","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5fiyy74","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"受光于隙见一床，受光于窗见室央，受光于庭户见一堂，受光于天下照四方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0yagoyb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0yagoyb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6k54il2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6k54il2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马不可以服重，牛不可以追速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3u8omiq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3u8omiq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-humlzlq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-humlzlq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改过不吝，从善如流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-beoxvng","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-beoxvng","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-mt13akh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mt13akh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚负凌云万丈才，一生襟抱未曾开。鸟啼花落人何在，竹死桐枯凤不来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-x5qh5a6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x5qh5a6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-f1u5yxg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-f1u5yxg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兰生幽谷，不为莫服而不芳；舟在江海，不为莫乘而不浮；君子行义，不为莫知而止休。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-89kq8pb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-89kq8pb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-8vx8k7x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8vx8k7x","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一日不思量，也攒眉千度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0s5883n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0s5883n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-t2plu5o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-t2plu5o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"彊弩之极，矢不能穿鲁缟；冲风之末，力不能漂鸿毛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7b1mvbl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7b1mvbl","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9zstgch","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9zstgch","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时来天地皆同力，运去英雄不自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-39jgrae","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-39jgrae","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-qnfzlpv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qnfzlpv","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"倒持干戈，授人以柄。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9citful","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9citful","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-6qhbyp7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-6qhbyp7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生一世，草生一春。来如风雨，去似微尘。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-mk6s3x4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mk6s3x4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-y9txjlf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-y9txjlf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪莱：未来不足惧，过往不须泣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b6wgwun","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b6wgwun","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-d3vrfdn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-d3vrfdn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从善如登，从恶如崩。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-p6i9ja1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p6i9ja1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tig3c0s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tig3c0s","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春生、夏长、秋收、冬藏，天之正也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-c3yis5n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-c3yis5n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-29ooe28","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-29ooe28","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前事不忘，后事之师。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-g6kffkp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-g6kffkp","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-3sl3xst","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3sl3xst","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逢人不说人间事，便是人间无事人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-kdmxvh9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kdmxvh9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-za44071","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-za44071","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"花开花落树之常，能上能下人中强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yar2iue","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yar2iue","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-otzsugc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-otzsugc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立品同白玉，读书到青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-sw89rka","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-sw89rka","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fjw0whn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fjw0whn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陀思妥耶夫斯基：爱具体的人，不要爱抽象的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-m5hh51d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m5hh51d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-7x086iu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7x086iu","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凭君莫话封侯事，一将功成万骨枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-m1xmnqg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-m1xmnqg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-duutskd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-duutskd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下皆知美之为美，斯恶已。皆知善之为善，斯不善已。有无相生，难易相成，长短相形，高下相盈，音声相和，前后相随，恒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-2krai1f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-2krai1f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zyjauee","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zyjauee","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子之心事，天青日白，不可使人不知；君子之才华，玉韫珠藏，不可使人易知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5305nwf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5305nwf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hc4ftpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hc4ftpr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除掉荒草的最好办法，不是让除完草的土地荒着，而是种上庄稼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nbety36","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nbety36","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-lu33d8w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lu33d8w","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善战者，求之于势，不责于人。故能择人而任势。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ehjsfuj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ehjsfuj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-l63tash","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l63tash","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"川泽纳污，所以成其深；山岳藏疾，所以就其大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0us51hm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0us51hm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zsitq93","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zsitq93","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"覆水不可收，行云难重寻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-lsg8v78","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-lsg8v78","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ipekeso","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ipekeso","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相鼠有皮，人而无仪！人而无仪，不死何为？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-v1zzypm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-v1zzypm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hbfrfyd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hbfrfyd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zdpbeu7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zdpbeu7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9euozrm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9euozrm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"狡兔死，走狗烹；飞鸟尽，良弓藏；敌国破，谋臣亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5xwlws4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5xwlws4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ct4kzhb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ct4kzhb","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马丁·路德·金：我们这一代人终将感到悔恨，不仅仅因为坏人的可憎言行，更因为好人的可怕沉默。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nk33uq8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nk33uq8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-icybu5v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-icybu5v","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我本将心向明月，奈何明月照沟渠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-52e0y0f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-52e0y0f","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-mhjl8yl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mhjl8yl","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网；扬汤止沸，不如去火抽薪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8m8gpoa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8m8gpoa","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5wjdh3p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5wjdh3p","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"芳林新叶催陈叶，流水前波让后波。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ez48vyk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ez48vyk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-otkn8gz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-otkn8gz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日出扶桑一丈高，人间万事细如毛。野夫怒见不平处，磨损胸中万古刀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ztq0cj0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ztq0cj0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kk7hthn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kk7hthn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：果实的事业是尊贵的，花的事业是甜美的，但是让我做叶的事业吧，叶是谦逊地、专心地垂着绿荫的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bsl3708","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bsl3708","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nhtjgum","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nhtjgum","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子耻不修，不耻见污。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0dt8wxk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0dt8wxk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zwio4p1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zwio4p1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陶行知：做学问就是要学要问。光学不问，只做到一半；光问不学，也只是一半。又学又问，才是完整的学问。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3rnij70","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3rnij70","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fadql9g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fadql9g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恶不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jf3d655","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jf3d655","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-diom53a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-diom53a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众里嫣然通一顾，人间颜色如尘土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1p0hwhk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1p0hwhk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-u5owei9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u5owei9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将者，智、信、仁、勇、严也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-zhrd1ig","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zhrd1ig","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-p51p9j8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p51p9j8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍：才华是刀刃，辛苦是磨刀石。很锋利的刀刃，若日久不用石磨，也会生锈，成为废物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-szknz6g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-szknz6g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-o1nzjwt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-o1nzjwt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少年侠气，交结五都雄。肝胆洞，毛发耸。立谈中，死生同。一诺千金重。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-61ulxk1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-61ulxk1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-biracqi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-biracqi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰 ：一个人的绝对自由是疯狂，一个国家的绝对自由是混乱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0t3hl3l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0t3hl3l","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e6244ko","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e6244ko","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学然后知不足，教然后知困。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wlrztw6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wlrztw6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-vjypyrz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vjypyrz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记人之长，忘人之短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-f61aqqc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-f61aqqc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ik2vwli","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ik2vwli","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知彼知己者，百战不殆；不知彼而知己，一胜一负，不知彼，不知己，每战必殆。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-f7gjq85","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-f7gjq85","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-a6vvwy4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a6vvwy4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"月缺不改光，剑折不改刚。月缺魄易满，剑折铸复良。势利压山岳，难屈志士肠。男儿自有守，可杀不可苟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-yibzzgf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-yibzzgf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zxf9cqt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zxf9cqt","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生贵相知，何必金与钱？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-evdq1zi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-evdq1zi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-l7zw2av","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l7zw2av","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有真才者，必不矜才。有实学者，必不夸学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-dyvxbow","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-dyvxbow","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-n0uh3fg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n0uh3fg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"薄我货者也，欲与我市者也；訾我行者，欲与我友者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b8x5x0s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b8x5x0s","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-obqk9mz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-obqk9mz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风乍起，吹皱一池春水。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-863mrry","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-863mrry","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-0qi6qf3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0qi6qf3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生万事须自为，跬步江山即寥廓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bma6de1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bma6de1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cgilyoi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cgilyoi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十年磨一剑，霜刃未曾试。今日把示君，谁有不平事？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-5zymxf3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5zymxf3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rsire8o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rsire8o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草木秋死，松柏独在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7mzv7d2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7mzv7d2","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-fp6z30h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-fp6z30h","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生是一匹马，轻快而健壮的马。人，要像骑手那样大胆而细心地驾驭它。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-mvwtkog","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-mvwtkog","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-5y1wgwr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-5y1wgwr","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"水广者鱼大，山高者树修。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-gnvkff7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-gnvkff7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-rfmfh5r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-rfmfh5r","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如梦，把梦看得太认真，固然是个大傻瓜；但以为人生如梦，就以为不必认真，也是个头等大傻瓜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hywdzuw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hywdzuw","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-pnf5gv1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pnf5gv1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一叶浮萍归大海，为人何处不相逢！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-tuesjgz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tuesjgz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-no0z6ep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-no0z6ep","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"力田不如逢年，善仕不如遇合。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-uwvxtwn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-uwvxtwn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-oyz9k5d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oyz9k5d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道路难行钱作马，城池不克酒为兵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-xiplz8g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xiplz8g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-8ufpqag","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8ufpqag","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古人云，“读书百遍，其义自见”。谓读得熟，则不待解说，自晓其义也。余尝谓，读书有三到，谓心到，眼到，口到。心不在此，则眼不看仔细，心眼既不专一，却只漫浪诵读，决不能记，记亦不能久也。三到之中，心到最急。心既到矣，眼口岂不到乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9gmdmmw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9gmdmmw","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-w5wak32","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-w5wak32","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知人者智，自知者明。胜人者有力，自胜者强。知足者富。强行者有志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nx3bt2q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nx3bt2q","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-8ikyvlf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8ikyvlf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"驿寄梅花，鱼传尺素。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ycm7jrg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ycm7jrg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-o94mh2r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-o94mh2r","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自然既极博大，也极残忍，战胜一切，孕育众生。蝼蚁蚍蜉，伟人巨匠，一样在它怀抱中，和光同见。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-i31a86d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-i31a86d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-vdwhwa7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vdwhwa7","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：与恶龙缠斗过久，自身亦成恶龙；凝视深渊过久，深渊将回以凝视。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-jt2x7n6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jt2x7n6","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-9dgamwl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9dgamwl","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天戴其苍，地履其黄，纵有千古，横有八荒，前途似海，来日方长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-qpe1sqq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qpe1sqq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-cih1tr5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-cih1tr5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子坦荡荡，小人长戚戚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-9i0gqpa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-9i0gqpa","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-jqgvje9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jqgvje9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心中有丘壑，眉目作山河。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-z9m97ap","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z9m97ap","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-x0ieoqz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-x0ieoqz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"寄蜉蝣于天地，渺沧海之一粟。哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ubhlq0k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ubhlq0k","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kx6n1vg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kx6n1vg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明代思想家袁了凡：昨日种种，譬如昨日死；今日种种，譬如今日生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-igubj75","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-igubj75","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-p5zt3ie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-p5zt3ie","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黑格尔：只有永远躺在泥坑里的人，才不会再掉进坑里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-siuiuh3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-siuiuh3","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-ppj5x0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ppj5x0n","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：每一个不曾起舞的日子都是对生命的辜负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bfj6qf5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bfj6qf5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-khz9qgc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-khz9qgc","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子在齐闻《韶》，三月不知肉味，曰：‘不图为乐之至于斯也。’"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ithq4mz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ithq4mz","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xs2d6om","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xs2d6om","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：命定的局限尽可永在，不屈的挑战却不可须臾或缺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-33p0ekm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-33p0ekm","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-b4q8shj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b4q8shj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：当我走向你的时候，我原想收获一缕春风，你却给了我整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-7u36qu5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-7u36qu5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-xh3yj65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-xh3yj65","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：我相信，在群星当中有一颗星星，引领我的生命，穿越不可知的黑暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-18w6v65","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-18w6v65","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-jk17yi8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jk17yi8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：心晴的时候，雨也是晴；心雨的时候，晴也是雨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-a71z28z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-a71z28z","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-zk5sfq9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-zk5sfq9","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聂卫平：遇到顺势而下的时候，就一泻千里；遇到阻碍过不去的时候，就绕一下，但我的目标一直是向前走的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-nbltmqd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nbltmqd","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-nyme3hs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-nyme3hs","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曼德拉：我没有失败过。要么赢得胜利，要么学到东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-8zugy3g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-8zugy3g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-33x6nq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-33x6nq5","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间是单程车票，我们只能向前；而记忆是随身行李，始终伴你同行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-oeg516o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-oeg516o","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e0zorgj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e0zorgj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"喷泉之所以漂亮，是因为它有压力；瀑布之所以壮观，是因为它没有退路；滴水之所以能穿石，是因为它贵在坚持。一只站在树枝上的鸟，从不害怕树枝会断裂，因为它相信的不是树枝，而是它自己的翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-48s6inf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-48s6inf","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kax9o24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kax9o24","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"追风赶月莫停留，平芜尽处是春山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-3f6ry25","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-3f6ry25","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-hfcq3jj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hfcq3jj","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼《浣溪沙·游蕲水清泉寺》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-b1k7ica","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-b1k7ica","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-e4jyz0a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-e4jyz0a","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朱敦儒《鹧鸪天·西都作》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-wd49br8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-wd49br8","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-tmuhyf4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-tmuhyf4","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杜甫《蜀相》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-vh0er0g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-vh0er0g","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-pxrurd1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-pxrurd1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《忆秦娥》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-hacyo8m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-hacyo8m","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-un4d368","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-un4d368","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《上李邕》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-0jdd7l1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-0jdd7l1","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-u22e1mh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-u22e1mh","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游《金错刀行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-4zwm4vk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-4zwm4vk","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-c5jvdbq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-c5jvdbq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李煜《虞美人》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-bfsueud","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-bfsueud","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-z6zb1u0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-z6zb1u0","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白居易《琵琶行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-n0vv89i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-n0vv89i","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-t27hmsn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-t27hmsn","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"礼记《大学》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-qqb002d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-qqb002d","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-kqib5tq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-kqib5tq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"范仲淹《岳阳楼记》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-1nt3tdi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-1nt3tdi","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-s4nu1mq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-s4nu1mq","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张若虚《春江花月夜》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-ijxb831","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-ijxb831","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-jogxrja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-jogxrja","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《侠客行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081148-itbmx2i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-itbmx2i","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081148-l9m8vbg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081148-l9m8vbg","updated":"20260605081148"},"Children":[{"Type":"Nod